=================================================
V2.00 of my map: aim_cod4_killhouse_mpn
=================================================

Basically it is more a remake of the mp_killhouse from call of duty 4
my goal doing this map was to replicate the original one 
I hope you enjoy it, beacuse it take me a quite long time to make it.

=================================================
- 16 spawnpoints
- Enable HDR
=================================================
V2 changes:

- soot changed (no more snow)
- new environment (lights, sun)
- fog removed
- small changes in the shadows
- minor changes
=================================================
comment, vote and download XD!
